Module edu.wgu.qam2schedulingapp
Package edu.wgu.qam2schedulingapp.helper

Class Logs

java.lang.Object
edu.wgu.qam2schedulingapp.helper.Logs
public class Logs extends Object
Logs is a utility class responsible for handling all log operations within the application. It provides methods to log information, warnings, errors, and login activity. All logged data is output to the console and stored in a text file for future reference.
Author:
Parham Modirniya

      public static void loginLog(String user, boolean isSuccessful)

      Parameters:
      user - the username of the user who attempted to login
      isSuccessful - true if the login was successful, false otherwise
